docs {
  ## Create Vendor
  สร้างผู้ขายใหม่

  Creates a new vendor/supplier in the business unit.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  - **Permission key**: `vendor_management.vendor:create`
  - **Roles**: Purchase

  ### Sample Body
  ```json
  {
    "code": "VND-2024-0001",
    "name": "Siam Fresh Co., Ltd.",
    "business_type": ["019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4e"],
    "description": "Fresh produce and food ingredients supplier",
    "info": [
      { "label": "Tax ID", "value": "0105562034871", "data_type": "string" }
    ],
    "vendor_address": {
      "add": [
        {
          "address_type": "mailing_address",
          "address_line1": "88/12 Mu 4, Phahonyothin Road",
          "city": "Pathum Thani",
          "postal_code": "12120",
          "country": "Thailand"
        }
      ]
    },
    "vendor_contact": {
      "add": [
        {
          "name": "Wannapa Srisuwan",
          "email": "wannapa.s@siamfresh.co.th",
          "phone": "0812345678",
          "is_primary": true
        }
      ]
    }
  }
  ```

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 201,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 400 | `name` or `code` is missing or invalid |
  | 401 | Missing or invalid bearer token |
  | 403 | User lacks `vendor_management.vendor:create` permission |
}
